text: Safa Saidani (born 26 May 1990) is a Tunisian table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's singles event, in which she was eliminated in the preliminary round by Dina Meshref. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Tunisian female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Tunisia Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Competitors at the 2019 African Games Category:African Games bronze medalists for Tunisia Category:African Games medalists in table tennis Category:African Games competitors for Tunisia
